Package: ldccr
Title: Utilities for Various Japanese Corpora
Version: 0.1.0.20230706
Authors@R: 
    person("Akiru", "Kato", , "paithiov909@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Akiru Kato <paithiov909@gmail.com>
Description: The goal of ldccr package is to make easy to use Japanese
    language resources. This package provides parsers for several Japanese
    corpora that are free or open licensed and a downloader of zipped text
    files published on Aozora Bunko.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/paithiov909/ldccr
BugReports: https://github.com/paithiov909/ldccr/issues
Depends: 
    R (>= 2.10)
Imports: 
    dplyr,
    memoise,
    purrr (>= 1.0.0),
    RcppSimdJson,
    readr,
    rlang,
    stringi,
    tibble,
    utils,
    yesno
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
